# Quick Revision

| Operator           | Purpose                                           |
| ------------------ | ------------------------------------------------- |
| `$expr`            | Compare fields or perform calculations in queries |
| `$match`           | Filter documents                                  |
| `$group`           | Group documents                                   |
| `$sum`             | Calculate total                                   |
| `$avg`             | Calculate average                                 |
| `$count`           | Count documents                                   |
| `$project`         | Select or modify fields                           |
| `$sort`            | Sort documents                                    |
| Embedded Documents | Store documents inside documents                  |
| Projection         | Control returned fields                           |
